      "name": "Non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw applicability domain",
      "description": "Model is applicable to solid (non-cannulated) titanium-alloy pedicle screws with nominal outer diameter 7.0–8.0 mm, thread pitch 2.75–3.25 mm, and construct length 40–50 mm tested under ASTM F1717 static compression-bending loading. Extrapolation to cannulated designs, diameters outside this range, or dynamic loading conditions is explicitly excluded from this COU."
    },
    "hasOperatingEnvelope": {
