      "name": "ASTM F1717 static compression-bending operating envelope",
      "description": "Applied compressive load: 0–2500 N; crosshead displacement rate: 5 mm/min ± 0.5 mm/min; ambient temperature: 23 ± 2 °C; UHMWPE block geometry per F1717-21 Annex A1; screw insertion torque: 6.0–8.0 N·m; construct angulation: 7° ± 0.5°. Model inputs must lie within these bounds for the credibility assessment to remain valid."
    }
  },
